snippet.title: Fit For a King Announcement Trailer - Henry VIII Simulator
snippet.description:
Marry everything. Execute everything. Spend it all! The world's finest, most historically accurate Henry VIII simulator. Humiliate the king of France by outspending him at the Field of Cloth of Gold... or die trying.

Wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1110380/Fit_For_a_King/
